    "date": "2021-04-14T16:12:21Z",
    "text": "Protecting Homeowners in Bankruptcy Act of 2021\n\nThis bill increases the homestead exemption an individual debtor can claim in a bankruptcy to $100,000. The homestead exemption allows a debtor to exempt from property of the estate the debtor's interest in property used as the debtor's residence or interest in a burial plot for the debtor."
